#Dataset information:

https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/iris 

#Attribute Information:
   1. sepal length in cm
   2. sepal width in cm
   3. petal length in cm
   4. petal width in cm
   5. class: 

      -- Iris Setosa -- represented as 0

      -- Iris Versicolour -- represented as 1

      -- Iris Virginica -- represented as 2
